<br>
There would have to be a penalty for being in full aggressive mode, and if you are able to instantly switch out, there isn't. <br>
<br>
3 levels: aggressive, normal, defensive. You can switch from aggressive or defensive to normal, but not directly from defensive to aggressive, or vice versa. Make a timer that allows you to switch at most every 1?3? minutes. Have them change offense/defense by +20%/-20%, 0/0, -20%/+20%. There would be a real penalty for being caught in the wrong mode.<br>
