Enraging blow type aa ability: could use say once every 50 sec to 2 mins. A one time hit that adds the same ammount of hate that a single proc of an eb weapon would give. This would still leave those weapons highly desired as it would give you more hate overall but this AA would give a warrior the chance to grab a significant amount of hate right off the bat at the beginning of a pull.<br>
<br>
AA ability to give us effects on our hits at random, such as for example similar to crits and crips:<br>
<br>
Hits that cause a bleeding effect like a dot ( call it Critical Strike)<br>
