Hits that cripple a mob as in breaking bones etc.... ( Bonecrusher)<br>
<br>
Hits that stun a mob at random while generating an appropriate amount of hate.(Dazing Strike)<br>
<br>
Pre 60 in non pop zones these things are not needed.<br>
